{"tid":2174361,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯算唔算是敗走西甲，恥辱離隊","createTime":"2020-08-26T00:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T06:34:07.000Z","uid":43785,"like":44,"dislike":157,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"6aadb4d350add0abe3d0b38193ff47de3ddf1e32","tid":2174361,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:20:37.000Z","msg":"好老實，足球上，我美斯踢波真係數一數二<br />\n，但論智慧，佢真係冇咩頭腦。<br />\n<br />\n係最高峰離隊真係冇人會話佢，偏偏今年冇左西甲，歐聯俾人大炒的時候恥辱離開。<br />\n<br />\n佢永遠在最不應離隊的時候宣布離隊，總是咁樣做，俾人感覺輸唔起/敗走西甲，<br />\n美洲盃又係咁，一輸波就話要退出國家隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解你唔可以醒少少呀，美斯。<br />\n點解唔可以贏住西甲之後光榮離隊，偏偏要輸撚咗個西甲先走呀。<br />\n我唔洗你三連霸，最少你贏個歐聯先走都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我之前仲一直讚你，呢十幾年無論人地開咩價都唔走，因為對球隊忠心。<br />\n屌，依家主動走，我點樣同你兜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴塞又係，之前一直J緊有人情味，<br />\n恥笑皇馬，卡斯拿斯無情雞，依家牙蘇話唔想走，要做後備帶新人都寧願付清條數都唔俾人做後備。其實佢仍然有世界一線前鋒既水平。<br />\n美斯服務咁多年，冇功都有勞，人地要走點解唔可以好來好去，係都要要告鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美斯敗走西甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />敗走歐聯，敗走阿根廷<br />\n一直令我地呢D支持你既球迷失望，依家仲要恥辱離隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實你幾時先生性，可以踢場好波，令球迷開心返呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW即使敗走西甲都好，我地永遠支持美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6Zo6nb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH6Zo6nb.jpg&h=f620b0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢想走就好了，我好想佢下一站去曼城拿英超挑戰自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083ff41bebce94418eed471ce70410da7327a6a9","tid":2174361,"uid":167721,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:21:09.000Z","msg":"你點離的"},{"pid":"53cc6f4e7f55f25abee89748f1dc99d3873a1cb0","tid":2174361,"uid":116455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:21:42.000Z","msg":"但我想睇佢挑戰意假多d"},{"pid":"963ea288950ac6bc5f48f20f867585b4a520d594","tid":2174361,"uid":71376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:21:56.000Z","msg":"你點算的"},{"pid":"c18e7dceb146d04ae636be1c21760d55e2f70b0b","tid":2174361,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:24:09.000Z","msg":"終於去挑戰自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de6a1f1f17e5157bdc76940bb21428577d1e219","tid":2174361,"uid":10308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53cc6f4e7f55f25abee89748f1dc99d3873a1cb0","tid":2174361,"uid":116455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:21:42.000Z","msg":"但我想睇佢挑戰意假多d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:25:16.000Z","msg":"得psg同曼城呢d大財團先買得起"},{"pid":"4a297f60849882f068e2058cc52f3f7a3c2b255e","tid":2174361,"uid":116455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6de6a1f1f17e5157bdc76940bb21428577d1e219","tid":2174361,"uid":10308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53cc6f4e7f55f25abee89748f1dc99d3873a1cb0","tid":2174361,"uid":116455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:21:42.000Z","msg":"但我想睇佢挑戰意假多d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:25:16.000Z","msg":"得psg同曼城呢d大財團先買得起"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:26:08.000Z","msg":"而家唔係話有機免簽咩，差人工姐"},{"pid":"cfb2d13a563bed1d2817faa7d9130e29fbd6f9e3","tid":2174361,"uid":261873,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:26:52.000Z","msg":"3大球王都係敗走西甲<br />\nc朗 美斯 武磊"},{"pid":"6369621765f4e66334f9c76b17704770fdd84bf0","tid":2174361,"uid":43785,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"53cc6f4e7f55f25abee89748f1dc99d3873a1cb0","tid":2174361,"uid":116455,"like":2,"dislike":